25. Search Index Support
Search should index:
- exam names.
- subject names.
- chapter names.
- topic names.
- question text.
- explanations.
- learning content titles.

Recommended approach:
- Keep a search index table or external search engine.
- Rebuild indexes asynchronously via queue jobs.

